  • Classes in com.github.alinaioanaflorea.xmldiff.core.model used by com.github.alinaioanaflorea.xmldiff.core.model 
    Class and Description
    ModificationType
    This enumeration holds values that reflect the changes done to an XML element:

    - SAME - it did not changed
    - MANDATORY - is a mandatory element so it will be kept in the output file even if its content did not changed
    - CHANGED - it changed
    - NEW - is missing from the application's first input file
    - DELETED - is missing from the application's second input file

    Precedence rules:
    - NEW and DELETED have priority over other states
    - CHANGED has priority over SAME and MANDATORY
    - MANDATORY has priority over SAME
    XmlAttribute
    This class represents the attribute of an XML element
    XmlElem
    This class represents an XML element
    XmlNode
    This class represents an XML node
    XmlNodeMetaData
    This class provides meta data for an XmlNode structure:
    - how did its content change
    - the indexes of the XmlNode's parent structures, if it was built from other XmlNodes,
    and the percentage at which they matched

    The indexes refer to the XML structures created from the application's input files.
